<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>{% block title %}Welcome{% endblock %} — Ayra</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,400;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg1: #0f0a1a;
            --bg2: #1a1240;
            --accent: #8b5cf6;
            --accent2: #22d3ee;
            --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            --text: #f4f4f5;
            --muted: #a1a1aa;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "DM Sans", system-ui, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background: radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 10% -10%, #3b1f6b 0%, transparent 55%),
                        radial-gradient(900px 600px at 100% 0%, #0e7490 0%, transparent 50%),
                        linear-gradient(165deg, var(--bg1) 0%, var(--bg2) 45%, #0c1222 100%);
        }
        .wrap {
            max-width: 52rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem) 1.5rem 4rem;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.35);
            padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.75rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .lead {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0 0 2rem;
            max-width: 38rem;
        }
        .cards {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1.35rem 1.5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }
        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .card p {
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .card a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.35rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--accent2);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .card a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.35rem;
            border-radius: 0.65rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #6366f1 100%);
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.35);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: var(--text);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }
        .edit {
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .edit h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .edit p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 40rem; }
        .edit .links { margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; }
        .edit .links a {
            color: var(--accent2);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
    <span class="badge">Ayra bundle</span>
    <h1>Your Pimcore stack is running</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        This page replaces the empty skeleton document view. Use Studio for data objects or open the classic admin when you need it.
    </p>

    <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Pimcore Studio</h2>
            <p>Modern UI for documents, assets, and data objects.</p>
            <a href="/pimcore-studio/">Open Studio →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Admin UI</h2>
            <p>Classic Pimcore backend and configuration.</p>
            <a href="/admin">Open admin →</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/pimcore-studio/">Launch Studio</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/admin">Admin</a>
    </div>

    {% if editmode %}
        <div class="edit">
            <h2>Editing in Pimcore</h2>
            <p>
                You are in <strong>edit mode</strong>. Add content to this document in the admin, or install sample data from the
                Pimcore docs if you want a full demo theme.
            </p>
            <div class="links">
                <a href="https://pimcore.com/docs/platform/Pimcore/Getting_Started/Installation/Webserver_Installation" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sample data / boilerplate</a>
                <a href="https://pimcore.com/docs/platform/Pimcore/Getting_Started" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Getting started</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
</div>
</body>
</html>
